Create, Relax, and Enjoy in 3 Simple Steps

Unwind and let your creativity flow. With just three simple steps, you can enjoy the satisfaction of crafting something uniquely yours. The Customizer Engraving Pen makes it effortless to create pieces that not only youll love but that will also impress everyone who sees them.

1. Choose Your Surface

Pick an item that you want to transformwhether its wood, glass, metal, or stone. The versatility of engraving means you can personalize almost anything.

2. Create In Calm

Sit back, relax, and let your creativity flow. As you engrave, enjoy the calming rhythm of the process, turning your ideas into reality.

3. Enjoy Your Achievement

Reflect on the piece youve created, and take pride in your work. Enjoy the sense of accomplishment and fulfillment that comes from crafting something truly your own.

Frequently Asked Questions

Still have questions? We have the answers.

Title

Will The Customizer take my crafting to the next level easily?

Absolutely! The Customizer makes it simple to elevate your crafting. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced crafter, this versatile engraving pen is designed to make creativity easy and accessible. You can effortlessly engrave, carve, and personalize materials like metal, wood, glass, and plastic. With attachments for sanding, polishing, and finishing, it helps you achieve professional-quality results without the hassle. The Customizer is your go-to tool for unlocking new creative possibilities and taking your projects to the next level with ease!

Is it beginner-friendly?

Yes! Whether you're a pro or just starting out, The Customizer is your go-to tool for making creativity simple. The more you use it, the more impressive your results will bebut no matter your skill level, this tool makes every project easier and more fun than ever

Is The Customizer safe for children to use?

Yes, kids and teens over 12 can definitely use The Customizer, as long as they have adult supervision. 

What are the shipping times?

United States: 5-7 calendar days for Customizer-only orders.
Rest of the World: 7-15 calendar days.
*Delivery times may vary by country. For more details, check our shipping policies here.

Whats in the Customizer box?

Your Customizer package includes everything you need to unleash your creativity:
- 1 Customizer tool
- 1 Carbide Burr
- 1 Hex key

- Pen Cap Cover

- User Manual
- 30 Diamond Bits
- 1 USB-C cable
- 4 Practice canvases (Acrylic, Bamboo, Eco-leather, Aluminum)

Are there attachments and accessories available for The Customizer?

We offer a range of engraving bits and accessories to help you unlock new creative possibilities and achieve different effects and styles with The Customizer. Check out our store to explore all the options!

What is the Mastery Guide and what's in it?

The Mastery Guide is your go-to resource for getting the best results with The Customizer. Packed with expert tips, creative ideas, and troubleshooting advice, it helps you easily engrave on different surfaces and use various engraving bits like a pro. Whether you're looking for inspiration or need a quick fix, this guide makes it simple to elevate your creativity and enjoy every project.
